IAL BIOLOGY SPECIFICATION
Pearson Edexcel International Advanced Level Biology
Specification Issue 2

============================================================
QUALIFICATION STRUCTURE
============================================================

IAS = Unit 1 + Unit 2 + Unit 3
IAL = Unit 1 + Unit 2 + Unit 3 + Unit 4 + Unit 5 + Unit 6

All units are externally assessed by written examination.
Calculators are allowed in examinations.

Minimum maths requirement:
At least 10% of marks across the qualification target Level 2 maths or above.

Core practicals:
18 core practical activities are included across the full specification.

